data.description: NO HOA and includes a tornado shelter!! Exquisite 4-Bedroom Home in the charming Kingswood neighborhood! This spacious gem boasts 2,363 square feet of comfortable living space and is situated on a generous .25-acre lot. The main level features beautiful laminate floors throughout, providing both elegance and easy maintenance. The heart of the home is the stunning kitchen with granite countertops and ample cabinetry. The primary bedroom suite is a sanctuary of luxury, featuring a jetted tub for ultimate relaxation. Three additional well-appointed bedrooms provide plenty of space for family and guests. One of the standout features of this property is the bonus room above the 2-car garage; offering endless possibilities, whether you choose to use it as a home office, gym, or media room. Rate as low as 6.25% available. Terms and Conditions apply.
